listitem.simpara:
AddGeometryColumn - Changed: 2.0.0 This function no longer updates geometry_columns since geometry_columns is a view that reads from system catalogs.  It by default
			also does not create constraints, but instead uses the built in type modifier behavior of PostgreSQL.  So for example building a wgs84 POINT column with this function is now 
			equivalent to: ALTER TABLE some_table ADD COLUMN geom geometry(Point,4326);
